;SEVCONFIELD DESCRIPTION=Bit 13: Enable current control gain scheduling (configure in 0x4641, 52-54)
;SEVCONFIELD DESCRIPTION=Bit 14: Allow PMAC voltage vector to move in all quadrants (PMAC geometric only)
;SEVCONFIELD DESCRIPTION=Bit 15: Use Gen5 torque conditioner (Gen5 only)
